    "Feeds" : {
      "comment" : "Tab bar title"
    },
    "Feeds are where minutes disappear. Not evil, not good — just expensive. But the fact is that they drain the color from the day. In this app, the more you open your banned apps, the less colorful your canvas becomes. Note that." : {
      "comment" : "Note body"
